---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Testimonials & Reviews for Restaurants — SocialProof" description="Turn happy diners into repeat business. Collect real testimonials from your guests and display them on your restaurant's website — free for one widget." canonical="https://socialproof.dev/for/restaurants">
<style>

    .hero { padding: 80px 24px 56px; text-align: center; max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 2.8rem; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; color: #111; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.25rem; color: #555; margin-bottom: 36px; }
    .hero .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 14px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .why-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .why-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; text-align: center; }
    .why-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr)); gap: 28px; margin-top: 40px; }
    .why-card { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px; }
    .why-card h3 { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .why-card p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; }
    .own-your-reviews { background: #fff8f0; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .own-inner { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .own-inner h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .own-inner p { font-size: 1.05rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .quote-section blockquote { font-size: 1.3rem; font-style: italic; color: #333; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .quote-section cite { font-size: 0.9rem; color: #888; }
    .cta-section { background: #111; color: #fff; padding: 60px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .btn-primary { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-secondary { background: transparent; color: #111; border: 1.5px solid #ccc; padding: 13px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    .btn-white { background: #fff; color: #111; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; }
    nav { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 16px 24px; }
    .nav-inner { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .logo { font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.2rem; text-decoration: none; color: #111; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { text-decoration: none; color: #555; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .btn-nav { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff !important; padding: 8px 18px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; }
    footer { border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding: 32px 24px; text-align: center; }
    footer a { color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 12px; }
    .steps-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .steps-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .step { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-bottom: 32px; align-items: flex-start; }
    .step-num { background: #6c47ff; color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .step-content h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .step-content p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
    .faq-section { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
    .faq-section h2 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; padding: 20px 0; }
    .faq-item h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #111; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .faq-item p { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }
    .social-proof-strip { background: #f5f5f5; padding: 40px 24px; text-align: center; }
    .social-proof-strip p { color: #888; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .social-proof-strip strong { color: #111; font-size: 1.1rem; }
</style>

<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="logo">SocialProof</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/for/yoga-studios">Yoga Studios</a>
      <a href="/for/contractors">Contractors</a>
      <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
      <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-nav">Get started free</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Turn happy diners into<br/>repeat business</h1>
  <p>Collect real testimonials from your guests and display them where it matters — your website, reservation page, and social media. No tech skills needed.</p>
  <div class="cta-group">
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Collect your first testimonial free</a>
    <a href="/tools/testimonial-wall-generator" class="btn-secondary">See a live example</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why-section">
  <h2>Why restaurants use SocialProof</h2>
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>🍽️ Own your reviews — don't rent them</h3>
      <p>Yelp and Google own their reviews. A single algorithm change can bury your 4.8-star rating. SocialProof testimonials live on your site, under your control, forever.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>📅 Fill tables on slow nights</h3>
      <p>A genuine quote from a happy diner — "Best pasta in Austin, we come every Friday" — on your reservation page converts better than any coupon. Real words from real guests.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>🔁 Drive repeat visits</h3>
      <p>Email your guests after a great experience. A short "Thank you — would you share a few words?" lands in their inbox and brings them back. Automated, one-time setup.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>🏆 Stand out on Google</h3>
      <p>Rich testimonial content on your website helps Google understand what your restaurant is known for — "romantic anniversary dinner," "best brunch," "gluten-free options" — and rank you for it.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>💬 Beat the big chains</h3>
      <p>Corporate chains spend millions on ads. Independent restaurants win on authenticity. Real voices from real guests in your neighborhood are your competitive edge.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <h3>⚡ Ready in 5 minutes</h3>
      <p>Paste one line of code to embed testimonials on your site. Or share a link. No developer, no monthly contract, no complicated setup.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="own-your-reviews">
  <div class="own-inner">
    <h2>Yelp and Google Reviews are not yours</h2>
    <p>Every review you earn on Yelp gets filtered, hidden, or buried by an algorithm you can't control. Google can suppress reviews with no warning. You've spent years earning that reputation — why leave it on someone else's platform?</p>
    <p>SocialProof gives you a direct line to your happiest guests. Send them a request, collect their words, display them on your site. Your reviews, your data, your brand.</p>
    <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-primary">Start collecting today — it's free</a>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="steps-section">
  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">1</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Share your collection link with guests</h3>
      <p>After a great meal, text or email your guest a link. They click, type a few sentences, done. No login, no friction. Takes them under 2 minutes.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">2</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Approve and display</h3>
      <p>Testimonials land in your dashboard. Approve the ones you love, reject the rest. Then embed a beautiful testimonial wall on your website with one line of code.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="step">
    <div class="step-num">3</div>
    <div class="step-content">
      <h3>Use them everywhere</h3>
      <p>Your testimonial widget works on any website — Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, or a custom site. Copy the embed code once and your newest reviews appear automatically.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="quote-section">
  <blockquote>"We started asking guests for testimonials after every private event. Within a month we had 12 quotes on our site. Bookings for private dining went up noticeably — people want to read real experiences before committing to a reservation."</blockquote>
  <cite>— Restaurant owner, Austin TX</cite>
</section>

<section class="faq-section">
  <h2>Questions from restaurant owners</h2>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Is this different from Yelp or Google Reviews?</h3>
    <p>Yes. Yelp and Google reviews are public platforms you have no control over. SocialProof testimonials are collected directly from your guests and displayed on your own website. You approve every testimonial before it goes live.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>How do I ask guests for testimonials without being pushy?</h3>
    <p>The best time is right after a great experience — a follow-up text or email 24 hours later. Something like: "It was great having you in. If you have 2 minutes, we'd love a few words: [link]." Our collection page is clean and takes under 2 minutes.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Will this work with my existing website?</h3>
    <p>Yes. SocialProof works with any website — Squarespace, Wix, WordPress, or a custom-built site. Paste one embed code and your testimonials appear automatically.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>What does it cost?</h3>
    <p>Free for up to 25 testimonials and one widget — enough to get started and see results. Pro is $9/month for unlimited testimonials, unlimited widgets, and no SocialProof branding.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Can I collect testimonials from past guests I already have emails for?</h3>
    <p>Yes. SocialProof has a bulk request feature — paste up to 100 guest emails and send them all a testimonial request at once. Perfect if you have a reservation history or email list.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="faq-item">
    <h3>Do my guests need to create an account?</h3>
    <p>No. Guests click a link, type their testimonial, and hit submit. No sign-up, no password, no friction. That's why the completion rate is high.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta-section">
  <h2>Start collecting testimonials today</h2>
  <p>Free for up to 25 testimonials. No credit card required. Set up in under 5 minutes.</p>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup" class="btn-white">Collect your first testimonial free →</a>
</section>

<footer>
  <a href="/">Home</a>
  <a href="/for/yoga-studios">Yoga Studios</a>
  <a href="/for/contractors">Contractors</a>
  <a href="/for/therapists">Therapists</a>
  <a href="/blog">Blog</a>
  <a href="/tools">Free Tools</a>
  <a href="https://app.socialproof.dev/signup">Sign up free</a>
</footer>

</Base>
